2:T6ec,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Canva better than Crello?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Canva scores 9.0 overall while Crello scores 6.0. Canva is best for non-designers and social media managers, while Crello excels for social media creators and small businesses."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Canva or Crello?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Canva starts at Free and Crello starts at Free. Canva offers a free plan. Crello offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Canva to Crello?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Canva and Crello support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Canva vs Crello?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Canva holds an overall rating of 9/10 and an ease of use score of 10/10. Crello has an overall rating of 6/10 and ease of use score of 7/10. Users praise Canva for incredibly easy to use for anyone and Crello for good animated design templates."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Canva or Crello?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Canva for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Crello remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize good animated design templates. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"compare-header","children":